            "body": "I've compared the output of dependency walker on Windows Server with and without the Desktop component.\r\n\r\nOn the system without desktop component, it seems that vcruntime140.dll is not found.\r\n\r\n\r\n![image](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/assets/11912465/b2480adb-bfa1-419d-8781-599edcb9e717)\r\n\r\n\r\nRight side is Windows Server 2022 without Desktop experience.\r\n\r\nShouldn't vcruntime140.dll get installed by the installer?",
